Transfer a WhatsApp Conversation from Marketing Cloud Engagement to Service Cloud with Journey Builder.

You can transfer a WhatsApp conversation from a Marketing Cloud Engagement interaction to a Service Cloud interaction. Place the WhatsApp Session Transfer activity after a Wait Until Chat Response or an Inbound Chat activity. The information passed as part of the transfer includes conversation history, journey data, the recipientâ€™s WhatsApp number, and the cross-cloud WhatsApp phone number.

title: Transfering WhatsApp Conversations between Marketing Cloud and Service Cloud
